text:
{'text': 'The service is very good, all of them are very nice. Atmosphere is very chilling too, good for friends to meet up. Has both indoor aircon seat and outdoor no aircon.
Food is definitely looking good and glamable.  Food taste good too, but for me half of 1 main is good enough.

Hot Bird : 7.6/10 Abit focus more on saltiness, but is still very sinfully great.
Patty Melt : 8.99/10 sour dough bread is very good combo with their beef. Sauce is good too.
Onion rings : 7.9 love it, onion taste is there.

Will come back again for their dinner set.', 'languageCode': 'en'}
